Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inherited will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The tide of the times... People's dreams...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These things cannot be stopped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as people seek the answer of freedom,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}these things will never cease to be!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:42.02,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,mirai dake shinjiteru dareka ga warattemo kamawanai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:47.52,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,hashitteru jounetsu ga anata o kiramekaseru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:53.53,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,mabushi sugi, demo mitsumete itai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:57.03,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,dokka "bigaku" kanjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.71,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,dare ni mo nitenai yume no senaka o
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.98,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,oikakete oikaketeku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.27,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,doramatikku te ni ireru made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:22.33,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,dare ni mo mienai yume no katachi o
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:25.39,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,tsukamaete tsukamaeteku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:31.40,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,watashi wa tsuite yuku kara atsui kimochi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.49,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,tsujitsuma awase betsu ni iranai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:37.84,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,arifureta nichijou yori mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.08,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,paradaisu mezashite hashire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:42.02,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I only believe in the future, I don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:47.52,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,that racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:53.53,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,it's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:57.03,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.71,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I follow, follow in the footsteps of a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.98,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.27,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:22.33,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:25.39,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,of a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:31.40,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go with you, so passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.49,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I don't really need everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:37.84,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.08,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.97,0:01:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind stopped again.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.72,0:02:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when we should be rushing \Nstraight for Little Garden, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're temporarily stopped again.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.77,0:02:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Time is running out as we speak, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.23,0:02:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we need to get to Alabasta \Nas soon as possible, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.36,0:02:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's fish! Fish!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.53,0:02:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, anyone seen the bait?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.82,0:02:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bait? Oh, the stuff in there? I ate it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.71,0:02:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You ate it?! Those were bugs, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.33,0:02:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? They taste good!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't eat stuff like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.88,0:02:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?! We can't fish now \Nthat you've eaten our bait!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.01,0:02:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this, then!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.22,0:02:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't catch anything with that!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.05,0:02:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? We can't?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.05,0:02:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about him?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. That sounds okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.47,0:02:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,– Hey, you! Come here!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.93,0:02:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,– Get back here, bait!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.68,0:02:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, you guys! Knock it off!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.48,0:02:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But can't {\i1}you{\i0} guys be a little worried, at least?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Worried about what?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.98,0:02:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! \NNami-{\i1}san{\i0} is lovely when she's angry, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, now!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.20,0:03:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.74,0:03:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For someone with a thirty-million-berry bounty,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.24,0:03:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,he doesn't seem that terrible of a person at all...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.25,0:03:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it might be hard to imagine, \Nbut he's beaten many big names.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.17,0:03:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Arlong, the Fishman who was \Nbent on ruling the East Blue...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.72,0:03:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirate Fleet Commodore, Don Krieg...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.72,0:03:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kuro, an unknown pirate \Nnotorious for his cunning methods.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.85,0:03:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot one.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A Navy freak who wields a huge axe-hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.27,0:03:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Axe-Hand Morgan!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.69,0:03:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Axe-Hand Morgan? \NI've heard of him before.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he's a Navy captain \Nwho's feared in the East Blue
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,for his overwhelming domination.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.16,0:03:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying he beat even him?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.49,0:03:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! The old axe-hand guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.21,0:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, I wonder what \Nthat guy with him is up to now...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.34,0:04:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's still at that Navy base...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's "he"?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.09,0:04:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! His name's Koby!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:19.36,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(352,110)}Try Hard, Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:19.36,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(352,455)}Koby-Meppo's \NStruggles in the Navy
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.32,0:04:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sub-Lieutenant! \NPreparations for departure are complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:27.24,Sign,,0,0,0,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All ships, move out!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.83,0:04:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Luffy-{\i0}san{\i1}! How are you? \NIt's me! Koby!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.55,0:04:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After we parted ways back then, \NI've worked my hardest!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There were plenty of hardships,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.01,0:04:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but now I've achieved my \Ndream of being a Navy officer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Captain Morgan!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.24,0:05:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Koby...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.08,0:05:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Hell, Koby!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.46,0:05:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya, Koby!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.14,0:05:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...Tornado!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.19,0:05:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! So pretty!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was dreaming!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.66,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! \NQuit screwing around, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.83,0:05:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.92,0:05:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.75,0:06:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep, you idiot chore boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:08.68,Sign,,0,0,0,,"Chore Boy"
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.47,0:06:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At any rate, Luffy-{\i0}san{\i1}, \NI'm now working at the Navy base!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.05,0:06:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Captain Morgan's son Helmeppo-{\i0}san{\i1} \Nwas given chore duty, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.31,0:06:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Quit slackin' off!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.40,0:06:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, chore boys! \NWash the windows when you're done cleaning!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.07,0:06:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't forget to clean up in the mess hall!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.11,0:06:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! What about {\i1}our{\i0} meal?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.99,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're obviously not gonna finish before lunch!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can eat after you've finished everything!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.45,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! But I'm starving to death here!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmeppo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.41,0:06:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmeppo! Koby!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.79,0:06:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.41,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both aware neither of you \Nwere qualified to join the Navy...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.00,0:06:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...yet you were given special \Npermission to join as chore boys, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.54,0:06:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like {\i1}you{\i0} let us join, though!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.55,0:06:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! Of course! \NIf there's anything I can do, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.80,0:06:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give the order!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.68,0:06:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No... just making sure you realize that.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.97,0:06:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Work hard, now!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.39,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! You can count on us!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.36,0:07:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll also be honored to do your laundry!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.06,0:07:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.77,0:07:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to go out of \Nyour way for even {\i1}more{\i0} work!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.78,0:07:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But we {\i1}are{\i0} chore boys, after all! \NOkay! Work! Work!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"We"?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.44,0:07:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna work that badly, \Nyou can do it yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.99,0:07:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,One! Two! Three! Four! \NOne! Two! Three! Four!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.67,0:07:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand this. \NForget Koby... why do {\i1}I{\i0} hafta be a chore boy?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.21,0:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How I wish I could go back to then...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmeppo-{\i1}sama{\i0}. Your cocoa, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.43,0:07:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Are you trying to scald me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sir! I-I'm very sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.19,0:07:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think I am?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.33,0:07:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Helmeppo-{\i1}sama{\i0}, only son of \Nthe great Navy Captain Morgan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.74,0:07:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! Helmeppo-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.25,0:08:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, things were good back then!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.67,0:08:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! \NThis is all that Straw Hat's fault!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.59,0:08:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He stripped Dad of his \Nposition as a Navy captain!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all his fault!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.31,0:08:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because of Straw Hat that \NI'm stuck doing this crap now!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.56,0:08:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmeppo-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.73,0:08:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?! \NDon't touch me all friendly-like!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.61,0:08:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. But I wanted to tell \Nyou something, as a friend...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.86,0:08:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Friend?! \NWhy would me and you be friends?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we {\i1}are{\i0} both chore boys...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.19,0:08:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the kind of guy who \Ndoes chores in a place like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If it hadn't been for Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.00,0:08:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good to blame Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0} \Nfor everything like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.92,0:08:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Blaming your fate on others won't solve anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.13,0:08:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you agree that's the sign of a weakling?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.76,0:08:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.10,0:09:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,For a long time, you lived your \Nlife using your father's power.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But from here on out, \Nwe need to face forward
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and search for our dreams on our own!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.57,0:09:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a dream!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.47,0:09:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, I {\i1}will{\i0} be a Navy officer \Nwho cracks down on bad guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be like that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.70,0:09:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A wimp like you, being a Navy officer?! \NThat'll never happen!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It will!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.42,0:09:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,After seeing how Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0} lives his life, \NI made up my mind!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.64,0:09:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.30,0:09:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to be it, so if I die \Nfighting for that, that's fine with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.13,0:09:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So I decided to be like Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0} \Nand put my life on the line
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to strive for my ambition!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.56,0:09:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You see? \NSo let's both work hard together!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.31,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.23,0:09:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0}, lecturing {\i1}me{\i0}?! \NSince when are you that high and mighty?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.15,0:09:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What could you possibly learn \Nfrom that despicable Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk bad about Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.03,0:09:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't said anything that's wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.24,0:10:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that were true, you still piss me off!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmeppo-{\i1}san{\i0}! \NPlease come to your senses!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you're anyone to talk!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.42,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! \NThe chore boys are fighting on the roof!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.39,0:10:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gawking for?! \NStop them already!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.86,0:10:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We're sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.54,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? \NThat explosion earlier was you guys' doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.08,0:10:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they kick you out of the Navy after that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.42,0:10:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.46,0:10:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we managed to avoid being kicked out.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.05,0:11:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to agree to work for free for 50 years, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.93,0:11:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Being kicked out would've been {\i1}much{\i0} better.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, you two!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! Look at this!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.80,0:11:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Straw Hat Luffy Wreaks Havoc in Loguetown!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.35,0:11:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Manages a Baffling Escape from Captain Smoker!"
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.90,0:11:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.19,0:11:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This means Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0} headed for the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.03,0:11:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, he's taken a big step \Ntoward realizing his dream!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.97,0:11:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now fill you in on our current mission!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.56,0:11:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whadya want?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.65,0:11:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dad...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.11,0:12:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Former Navy Captain Morgan is \Nto be sent to Navy Headquarters
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.32,0:12:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to face a court martial for the \Ncrimes of military exploitation
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and the tormenting of civilians!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.41,0:12:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,His transfer and delivery to \NVice Admiral Garp is today's mission!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.08,0:12:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Navy Captain "Axe-Hand" Morgan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.79,0:12:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You rankless, low-status \Nscum will kneel before me!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no getting around it, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.73,0:12:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He {\i1}should{\i0} get court-martialed or whatever else.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He does get what he deserves and all...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.07,0:12:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But to be honest, \NI still respected him anyways.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.45,0:12:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...was my idol.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.87,0:12:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess he did take things too far, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.72,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.89,0:13:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.06,0:13:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, do you think they'll execute him?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.66,0:13:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.86,0:13:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's no getting around that either, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.11,0:13:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Given how my dad is...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmeppo-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.08,0:13:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands on deck!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.59,0:13:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall in!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Vice Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Garp the Fist!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.81,0:13:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}he's{\i0} Navy Headquarters \NVice Admiral Garp the Fist!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.69,0:13:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The hero of the seas who \Ntravels all over the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.32,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Garp! \NThank you for coming all this way personally!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We hereby deliver Morgan to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.96,0:14:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.87,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,– Stop, Helmeppo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,– Umm... Vice Admiral Garp?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.54,0:14:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.22,0:14:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been up for five days now...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.52,0:14:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.43,0:14:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've been going for a \Nnew doughnut-eating record...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.18,0:14:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.56,0:14:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But the lack of sleep and rest has \Ngotten me a bit drowsy at 842...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This geezer's a joke.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.73,0:14:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Morgan! Vice Admiral Garp is a \Nleading figure at Navy Headquarters!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man. Cut the sleeping act.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.88,0:15:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Move and I'll hack this chore boy \Nup and feed him to the sharks!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.43,0:15:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,D-D-Dad!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.39,0:15:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop this! \NHelmeppo-{\i1}san{\i0} is your own son!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.06,0:15:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Son?! I don't need a son!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.82,0:15:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What I want is freedom! \NHis life means nothing to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll toss him into a pool of blood if I have to!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dad...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.24,0:15:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So long, fools!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmeppo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.87,0:15:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready the cannon!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.88,0:15:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Load! Aim!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.95,0:15:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Target... 16 degrees starboard! \NDistance... 8,263! Ready!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.76,0:15:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.89,0:16:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please don't shoot! My friend...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend's onboard!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.11,0:16:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.23,0:16:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll cut you down!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.41,0:16:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,– Stop, chore boy! \N– Don't go against regulations!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.16,0:16:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Helmeppo-{\i1}san{\i0} is my...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.24,0:16:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...my...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.91,0:16:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...friend!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.21,0:16:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That fool. Stirring up trouble, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.88,0:16:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}will{\i0} pay for this.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.77,0:16:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's much better than \Njust abandoning my friend!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.01,0:16:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I'll go capture him myself!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.11,0:16:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Come back! \NThere's no way you can catch him!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's let him go.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.87,0:17:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's either quite the fool, or...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.71,0:17:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.42,0:17:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with all the racket? \NI'm finally awake...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Garp! \NI thought for sure you'd been done in!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Someone's been done in?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.93,0:17:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see it because I was asleep! \NWho was wounded?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.32,0:17:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm free!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.79,0:17:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you watch! \NThe world will kneel down before me once again!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.91,0:17:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Today marks the new start of the newly reborn Morgan Kingdom!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.67,0:17:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Set our course to the west!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.63,0:17:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?! \NI said set our course to the west!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.30,0:17:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have no part in this!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.63,0:18:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He covered for me after this happened!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.31,0:18:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when getting kicked out of \Nthe Navy would destroy his dream!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.27,0:18:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's protecting me, regardless of that!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.73,0:18:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.73,0:18:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad! I'm going to capture you! \NJust give up-
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.94,0:18:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?! \NWho do you think you're talkin' to, huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.86,0:18:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What can a piece of useless scum do to me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.40,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as you're told, and I'll make \Nthings nice for ya. So be quiet and-
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.54,0:18:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up, Dad!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.83,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.67,0:18:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Know your place, you pathetic insect!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I'd ever listen to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.97,0:18:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} the one who decides how I live!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.76,0:18:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit getting the wrong idea! \NWhat can scum like you possibly do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.47,0:18:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't alone!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.64,0:18:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,M-M-Morgan!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give yourself up!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.86,0:18:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As a member of the Navy forces, \NI'm going to capture you!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.50,0:19:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic! Pathetic! Pathetic!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.14,0:19:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What can a couple of insects do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.29,0:19:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in my way and I'll chop you both into pieces!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.55,0:19:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry it turned out this way \Nafter you came to save me...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.51,0:19:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.10,0:19:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Koby...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.43,0:19:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I've made up my mind! \NI've decided to live for my beliefs!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.44,0:19:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A-And if I die fighting...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.28,0:19:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...if I die fighting for that, \Nthat's fine with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.45,0:19:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna die that badly, huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to die!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.54,0:19:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not until I've become a Navy officer! \NBut, when...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When I {\i1}do{\i0} die...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.13,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...it'll be...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...while I'm fighting!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Playtime is over!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Koby!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.72,0:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid idiot! Let Koby go! Koby!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.90,0:20:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn insects aren't even worth killing.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.53,0:20:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Never show yourself to me again!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.90,0:20:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Morgan!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.45,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you go for today!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.62,0:20:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But someday I {\i1}will{\i0} surpass you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, I {\i1}will{\i0} catch you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.04,0:20:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.88,0:20:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive my poor supervision!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.14,0:20:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Allowing the prisoner to escape \Nis the biggest blunder of my life!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.72,0:20:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're very sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.06,0:20:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,After what's happened, \Nthese two will be kicked out for life!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.98,0:20:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What truly lost causes you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.15,0:21:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt anyone anywhere would take you in now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.94,0:21:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'd only burden everyone \Nif we turned you loose...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.49,0:21:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You leave me no choice. \NCome with me to Navy Headquarters!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.28,0:21:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral! \NYou're going to take them with you to Navy HQ?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.08,0:21:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.08,0:21:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, not exactly...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.17,0:21:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two against it?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.05,0:21:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to run away, now's your chance.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.62,0:21:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I have no intention \Nof letting you say no, anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.26,0:21:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My, oh, my. \NWhat an odd day this has been!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.85,0:21:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that's how we wound up heading \Nfor the Grand Line, Luffy-{\i0}san{\i1}.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.45,0:21:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure the day will come when we meet again!{\i0}
